http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Thiruvananthapuram/Reception-planned-for-Ghulam-Ali/article13995797.ece

Chief Minister Oommen Chandy and CPI(M) State secretary Kodiyeri Balakrishnan will jointly present the ‘Swaralaya Global Legendary’ award to Pakistani ghazal singer Ghulam Ali at a function to be held at the Mascot Hotel here on Thursday evening.He will be accorded a rousing reception at the Thiruvananthapuram International Airport when he arrives here on Wednesday night.On Friday, Ghulam Ali will perform along with ghazal singer Pandit Viswanath and others at the Nishagandhi auditorium.Swaralaya and Tourism Department are jointly organising the events. On January 17, the singer will perform in Kozhikode.